snippet: Scotland's long debate over whether the country should become independent has proved a bonanza for printers of bumper stickers, posters, balloons and even umbrellas....

headline.print_headline: Debaters Hope to Sway Undecided in Scotland Vote
headline.main: Debaters Hope to Sway Undecided in Scotland Vote

lead_paragraph: Scotland's long debate over whether the country should become independent has proved a bonanza for printers of bumper stickers, posters, balloons and even umbrellas.
